(599, 1, '2025-10-18 09:25:10', '2025-10-18 09:25:10', '[section]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\" padding=\"50px 0px 50px 0px\"]\n\n[ux_text text_align=\"center\"]\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">I have a new Favourite Place in the World.</h1>\n<p><small>– DIVIA THANI, GLOBAL EDITORIAL DIRECTOR OF CONDE NAST TRAVELER –</small></p>\n<p><br />This is not simply an escape — it’s a return to life as it was meant to be. The journey to the Edge of Wildness is where untamed luxury meets boundless freedom. Just a short flight from Bali’s busy shores, Sumba Island — twice its size, with a fraction of its tourists — remains one of the world’s last untouched sanctuaries.Here, raw beauty and ancient culture create a canvas for meaningful journeys.<br /><br />A haven for adventurers, explorers, and curious souls.<br />Arrive with an open heart and immerse in rare moments of wonder. Depart transformed: refreshed, recharged, renewed.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'FRAME 2_ GIỚI THIỆU THƯƠNG HIỆU', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '597-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-10-18 09:25:10', '2025-10-18 09:25:10', '', 597, 'https://tram.websiteviet.net/?p=599', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
